---
description: Use when generating pull request descriptions, change summaries, or developer-facing explanations of code changes
---

When generating PR descriptions:

- summarize the purpose of the change clearly
- explain why the change was made
- group related changes together
- include testing notes when relevant
- mention risks, limitations, or rollback considerations
- avoid generic wording such as "updated code" or "made improvements"
- optimize for clarity and fast scanning
